  "detailed_description": "Be a bird, feed your hungry hatchlings, and avoid the dangers of the forest all year long!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Catch butterflies, worms, ladybugs, (and wasps, if you're a bluejay)<br></li><li>Avoid hazards like falcons, eagles, flying squirrels, wasps, and cats​<br></li><li>​Eat berries to get a speed boost -- but watch out for snakes!<br></li><li>​Use abilities unique to each bird, like getting sap from trees as a woodpecker<br></li><li>​Unlock bonus content through gameplay, like the beach level!<br></li><li>Each season features one of Vivaldi's 'The Four Seasons'​​ concerti</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914850/extras/57949bbdbb2e58f81f9f58e5ae9fb087.poster.avif?t=1750620027\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914850/extras/57949bbdbb2e58f81f9f58e5ae9fb087.webm?t=1750620027\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914850/extras/57949bbdbb2e58f81f9f58e5ae9fb087.mp4?t=1750620027\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Be a bird, feed your hungry hatchlings, and avoid the dangers of the forest all year long!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Catch butterflies, worms, ladybugs, (and wasps, if you're a bluejay)<br></li><li>Avoid hazards like falcons, eagles, flying squirrels, wasps, and cats​<br></li><li>​Eat berries to get a speed boost -- but watch out for snakes!<br></li><li>​Use abilities unique to each bird, like getting sap from trees as a woodpecker<br></li><li>​Unlock bonus content through gameplay, like the beach level!<br></li><li>Each season features one of Vivaldi's 'The Four Seasons'​​ concerti</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914850/extras/57949bbdbb2e58f81f9f58e5ae9fb087.poster.avif?t=1750620027\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914850/extras/57949bbdbb2e58f81f9f58e5ae9fb087.webm?t=1750620027\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914850/extras/57949bbdbb2e58f81f9f58e5ae9fb087.mp4?t=1750620027\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
